summary:
Hi, my name is Naysa. I am a Math teacher and I have being teaching for 15 years. I love teaching and writing. 

I moved to The Netherlands six years ago. Actually, I spend my time learning Dutch, coordinating my pet care company, teaching math for Dutch and international students, writing math content and doing volunteer work at an animal shelter. 

About math, I work writing Math content in English and Portuguese language. I also teach international and Brazilian students how come from Dutch or International schools, giving them online and in person private math classes. 

I am very attentive and responsive to my pupils, using educational methods that really could help my student to achieve their goals. 

As I am a pet lover, I decided  to open my own pet care company in Amsterdam. It is called Petzz Life and this business have been growing. 

I am open for new experiences in Math teaching and content producing. I hope my introduction clarifies about how I am. 

Thanks for reading.
